{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904290/extras/Resized-Steam-Gifs-Gamemode.gif?t=1732799429\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ROLL, ROLL, ROLL</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Roll your dice! Not once, not twice. Easily more than a thousand times!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With each roll, reveal tiles and earn points to enhance their value. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Throughout your journey, you will find many ways of gaining more rolls to reach the final location. None left? We go again!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904290/extras/Resized-Steam-Gifs-Roll.gif?t=1732799429\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ARTIFACTS &amp; LOCATIONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you try to conquer the challenging path ahead, you will be faced with many difficult decisions. Choose your path wisely and wield powerful artifacts that shape your strategy, presenting intriguing synergies along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904290/extras/Resized-Steam-Gifs-Relic.gif?t=1732799429\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SKINS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore new locations and unlock fresh tile skins, stunning visual effects or new satisfying sound packs. So even if your last run fell short, return to conquer in style!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904290/extras/Resized-Steam-Gifs-Skins.gif?t=1732799429\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GAMEMODES &amp; DIFFICULTIES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete the 'Standard' gamemode to unlock challenging variants, each with its own twists and turns. If you're in for a casual experience, you can lower the game's difficulty at any time, in every gamemode. And remember, no content is locked behind difficulty levels \u2014 every achievement is within your reach. </p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Champion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904290/5b3a78d2f5cab3d0cb5b85f0faea6c3f57449c81.jpg"},{"name":"Journey Champion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904290/8a9ac1bf2e939d4f92154c622c4917f7d8737b5f.jpg"},{"name":"Mayhem Champion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904290/23e9e491d88799ad8fbba755f55e03ec71b0afa7.jpg"},{"name":"Ultimate Champion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904290/845b93458d7c9837096ecc961db533f3fcc34dd4.jpg"},{"name":"Tile Gladiator I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904290/9f96ee4ddef60c13e5e20839a038abbbe0cdb16e.jpg"},{"name":"Tile Gladiator II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904290/4c3f247325543dee8bcdb8ba635b3e74654f93e0.jpg"},{"name":"Tile Gladiator III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904290/e40df50d003559d42f0575fda718e93ee44a5d0c.jpg"},{"name":"Tile Gladiator IV","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904290/604095abba2df376e958d28161b2d3262b676129.jpg"},{"name":"Predictable Roll","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904290/b7023b97c7932d667ede066d02ccb040be512a51.jpg"},{"name":"High Roller I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904290/1c2a70a6a449f855d2beba2755f5330698b01567.jpg"}],"total":31},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904290/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732799429","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com